  "texts": [
    "After the pilot interviews, we revised the questionnaire and adjusted our overall interview criteria.",
    "We ensured all participants at the outset that their anonymity and privacy would be safeguarded so that they would feel comfortable answering every question.",
    "Therefore, we abstained from requesting any personal identification information.",
    "In most cases, the participants were not interested in identifying themselves with personal information in the recording.",
    "Therefore, we recorded only interview responses related to this research."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}